WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.376 --> 01:37.680
=Episode 17=

01:40.138 --> 01:43.297
Are you two here
to see our shop's celadon?

01:44.498 --> 01:46.698
Could you please rest
in the private room next door?

01:47.097 --> 01:49.297
I'll have my men see to it

01:49.698 --> 01:53.138
and bring out all the finest celadon
from our shop.

01:53.817 --> 01:55.618
Aren't your rules very strict?

01:56.457 --> 01:59.537
I heard newcomers here must spend
ten thousand coins to see the best.

01:59.778 --> 02:00.938
It's my first time here.

02:00.938 --> 02:01.938
And you'll let me in?

02:03.418 --> 02:05.778
Rules are rigid,
but people are flexible.

02:06.177 --> 02:07.977
You two visiting is a great honor

02:08.257 --> 02:09.618
for our shop.

02:10.058 --> 02:11.417
Rules don't matter now.

02:12.458 --> 02:13.218
This way, please.

02:27.137 --> 02:30.218
I think this steward recognized me.

02:31.058 --> 02:32.018
Why do you say that?

02:32.857 --> 02:35.178
If he didn't know
I was the owner of Shende Shop,

02:35.498 --> 02:36.938
why would he be so attentive to me?

02:37.537 --> 02:40.058
He took me to the private room
and is about to show me the best.

02:40.977 --> 02:43.537
He probably wants to intimidate me
with his shop's treasure.

02:47.218 --> 02:48.178
Rest assured.

02:49.537 --> 02:52.178
The goods are ready. Please take a look.

03:06.218 --> 03:09.618
If these aren't to your liking,
there are more batches in the back.

03:11.738 --> 03:12.577
No need.

03:13.857 --> 03:14.778
Anything you like?

03:15.738 --> 03:17.218
We can have them all wrapped up.

03:18.898 --> 03:20.257
No need to hesitate to spend.

03:22.097 --> 03:25.577
This shop is mine.

03:27.857 --> 03:28.697
What?

03:30.697 --> 03:33.537
The shop owner
you mentioned just now is me.

03:35.417 --> 03:37.857
His Highness is indeed
the owner of our Jinbao Shop.

03:38.018 --> 03:40.458
I've served Prince Ding's household
for a long time.

03:47.218 --> 03:48.857
We do have some wealth.

03:49.618 --> 03:51.178
Why didn't you tell me before?

03:51.178 --> 03:53.778
Feng Zhiyao managed it before.
I didn't pay much attention.

03:54.417 --> 03:57.778
If you're interested, I'll hand it
all over to you.

03:58.817 --> 04:01.377
I'm interested.
I'm very much interested.

04:04.257 --> 04:05.618
Congratulations!

04:05.977 --> 04:09.338
In the future,
I'll rely on you for guidance.

04:22.098 --> 04:25.098
I think you're very different today.

04:33.520 --> 04:36.656
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

04:57.938 --> 04:58.618
Marquis Muyang.

04:59.618 --> 05:02.457
Gongshu Yang
found about my former guard.

05:02.457 --> 05:03.377
What happened exactly?

05:04.137 --> 05:05.498
Before reaching Huaixi,

05:05.498 --> 05:07.058
he first conducted an undercover visit.

05:07.377 --> 05:09.817
Then he had the major families
anonymously accuse each other,

05:09.817 --> 05:11.098
causing widespread panic.

05:11.897 --> 05:14.618
Everyone thought their secrets
had been exposed.

05:14.618 --> 05:17.897
After some pushing and shoving,
they pushed Guard Qiu out.

05:19.457 --> 05:20.618
But Marquis, rest assured.

05:21.017 --> 05:23.457
A man no family wants
is bound to die soon.

05:23.618 --> 05:25.098
Gongshu Yang won't get anything.

05:32.257 --> 05:34.418
Marquis, I...

05:35.257 --> 05:38.538
I was meant to become Adjutant Commander
of Zhechong Prefecture today.

05:39.697 --> 05:41.337
Why hasn't there been any news?

05:46.817 --> 05:49.577
There's been a slight hiccup
with that matter.

05:49.777 --> 05:50.978
I forgot to tell you.

05:51.618 --> 05:54.098
That post was taken by someone else.

05:56.017 --> 05:56.897
It's better not to go.

05:57.858 --> 06:00.538
Adjutant Commander of Zhechong
is always about fighting and killing.

06:00.738 --> 06:02.418
It's not really a good job.

06:03.098 --> 06:04.217
If you seek office,

06:04.538 --> 06:06.978
I'll find you a post elsewhere.

06:12.098 --> 06:13.017
Thank you, Marquis.

06:13.217 --> 06:15.538
It's been days in the capital.
Are you settling in?

06:16.137 --> 06:16.938
I'm fine.

06:21.618 --> 06:24.137
If you have any difficulties,
feel free to come to me.

06:32.697 --> 06:33.538
Guard Qin.

06:38.017 --> 06:38.538
Young Lord.

06:39.697 --> 06:42.897
Do you have time
to go to Xiangqi Pavilion for a drink?

06:44.377 --> 06:46.618
I still have official duties,
so I cannot drink.

06:48.257 --> 06:48.897
Farewell.

07:01.257 --> 07:02.498
What are you so happy about?

07:04.538 --> 07:05.337
Nothing.

07:06.418 --> 07:08.858
Don't you have official duties?
Go attend to them.

07:15.377 --> 07:17.938
I wasn't appointed to the post.
It was your doing?

07:20.098 --> 07:21.217
You seemed busy.

07:22.938 --> 07:24.098
So I eased your burden.

07:29.817 --> 07:30.658
Childish.

07:32.897 --> 07:36.017
Qin Zheng is nothing
like your cowardly father.

07:37.418 --> 07:40.137
The edict concerns her life
and everything she has.

07:40.538 --> 07:42.938
Getting her to talk is harder
than climbing to heaven.

07:44.457 --> 07:45.858
Of course we can't ask directly.

07:46.817 --> 07:47.618
You have a way?

07:48.577 --> 07:52.298
Dowager Consort Qin was close
to someone when she was in the palace.

07:55.017 --> 07:57.817
Zhou Xiankun, the official
from the Bureau of Astronomy?

07:58.178 --> 07:59.017
That's right.

07:59.978 --> 08:02.697
As far as I know, Zhou Xiankun

08:02.978 --> 08:05.377
had exceptional talent
and extraordinary insight,

08:05.618 --> 08:06.978
versed in five elements and stars.

08:07.377 --> 08:10.418
After the Empress Dowager,
he was who she respected most.

08:10.658 --> 08:12.978
So, you plan to start with him?

08:13.658 --> 08:14.377
Yes.

08:14.377 --> 08:15.777
But he passed away years ago.

08:16.418 --> 08:18.618
He's dead, but his disciples
are still around.

08:19.457 --> 08:20.858
They might know something.

08:23.817 --> 08:24.897
Be careful.

08:25.738 --> 08:26.938
Be careful.

08:27.658 --> 08:28.777
Take everything away.

08:28.777 --> 08:29.618
Leave nothing behind.

08:29.618 --> 08:30.577
Be careful.

08:32.418 --> 08:33.217
Alright.

08:33.337 --> 08:34.217
Be careful.

08:37.857 --> 08:38.658
Your Highness.

08:38.697 --> 08:39.857
What's going on?

08:40.138 --> 08:41.217
Your Highness doesn't know?

08:41.258 --> 08:42.617
My master said he won't come back.

08:42.697 --> 08:44.178
He wants it all sent back.

08:45.178 --> 08:47.378
Your Highness, if I may say so,

08:47.497 --> 08:49.737
only here a few days,
yet he has quite a lot of stuff.

08:49.737 --> 08:51.138
And he left without any notice,

08:51.418 --> 08:53.217
not even saying goodbye to you.

09:07.440 --> 09:09.840
(Longevity Shop)

09:11.538 --> 09:13.337
I told you our master isn't well.

09:13.817 --> 09:15.337
Please don't disturb him.

09:16.058 --> 09:16.938
What's wrong with him?

09:17.817 --> 09:20.018
Heat in his heart,
fire in his meridians.

09:20.058 --> 09:22.298
He can't eat or sleep.

09:22.658 --> 09:25.497
Anyway, he's unwell
and won't see outsiders.

09:29.778 --> 09:31.697
The 'outsiders' your master speaks of

09:32.058 --> 09:33.697
can't be just me, can it?

09:33.697 --> 09:35.497
Your Highness knows best in your heart.

09:35.577 --> 09:37.617
Our master simply
doesn't want to see you.

09:37.658 --> 09:39.258
That's why he had me stop you here.

09:39.737 --> 09:41.337
But honestly,

09:41.337 --> 09:42.658
you two are blood relatives.

09:42.697 --> 09:45.178
Say it at your residence
if you have private words.

09:45.457 --> 09:47.538
Why make it hard for me here?

09:48.538 --> 09:51.298
Don't worry.
I won't make it hard for you.

09:51.418 --> 09:54.457
Then Your Highness should go quickly.
I won't see you out.

09:55.418 --> 09:56.217
Ding.

09:58.298 --> 10:00.258
What are you doing? Let me go!

10:17.497 --> 10:18.298
Uncle Wenshen.

10:23.697 --> 10:25.337
I know you don't want to see me.

10:26.258 --> 10:29.697
But today, I have a reason
I must see you.

10:30.697 --> 10:34.217
If you won't open the door,
I'll just wait here until you do.

10:41.680 --> 10:45.552
(Sacred Tablet
of the Late Mother, Zhu Cenying)

10:48.658 --> 10:50.258
You moved all your things away.

10:51.138 --> 10:53.097
Not planning to return
to Prince Ding's Mansion?

10:55.857 --> 10:57.857
Prince Ding's Mansion's
threshold is too high.

10:59.577 --> 11:00.617
I dare not aspire to it.

11:00.898 --> 11:02.457
Are you blaming me?

11:12.697 --> 11:14.617
Wending was stripped
of his official post

11:15.337 --> 11:18.577
because he knowingly broke the law
and brought it upon himself.

11:19.178 --> 11:20.178
I don't blame you.

11:20.658 --> 11:22.138
Wenhua went mad

11:23.457 --> 11:26.977
because he wronged your mom
and got what he deserved.

11:29.298 --> 11:30.298
I don't blame you.

11:30.898 --> 11:32.418
Because of your mom's matter,

11:33.138 --> 11:34.977
you hate our entire Ye family

11:35.617 --> 11:39.058
and have thrown the Ye family
into chaos.

11:40.577 --> 11:41.817
I still don't blame you.

11:46.778 --> 11:48.298
But what about my mom?

11:49.898 --> 11:51.418
What did she do wrong?

11:51.778 --> 11:55.792
Perhaps you should
never have left the mountain.

11:58.938 --> 12:00.337
You want me to stay on Lishan.

12:01.138 --> 12:02.258
You're probably thinking,

12:02.977 --> 12:06.457
why couldn't I just die clean
like my mom did?

12:08.617 --> 12:09.778
I didn't say that.

12:09.778 --> 12:11.258
But that's exactly what you think.

12:16.298 --> 12:17.697
But it's understandable.

12:18.658 --> 12:19.577
After all,

12:20.097 --> 12:23.138
people always like to see things
from their own perspective.

12:23.857 --> 12:27.617
Even in the face of the law, it's hard
not to be blinded by family ties.

12:29.737 --> 12:33.457
But Uncle Wenshen,
I am also your family.

12:35.097 --> 12:36.938
You tacitly permitted them to do evil

12:37.258 --> 12:39.058
and turned a blind eye to their sins

12:39.737 --> 12:41.577
but can't tolerate
my act of self-preservation?

12:44.977 --> 12:48.097
I'd like to ask you:
what exactly did I do wrong?

12:49.138 --> 12:51.457
I also want to know
what exactly you did that night.

12:58.938 --> 13:02.497
If you have nothing to say,
please go ahead.

13:05.577 --> 13:08.658
I need to continue chanting sutras
for my mom.

13:26.898 --> 13:29.538
Uncle Wenshen, have some tea.

13:41.298 --> 13:45.058
You should know
about General Xiuwen's matter back then.

13:45.697 --> 13:48.592
(To whom did you give the edict
summoning Heiyun Cavalry to the capital?)

13:49.697 --> 13:51.378
Dowager Consort Qin.

14:10.058 --> 14:12.337
I never intended to harm Grandmother.

14:14.138 --> 14:15.977
She came at me with a blade.

14:17.658 --> 14:19.138
She wanted to get rid of me.

14:19.898 --> 14:22.497
Just like she killed my mom,
she wanted to kill me too.

14:22.898 --> 14:25.538
Was I supposed to just sit
and let her take my life?

14:30.497 --> 14:31.898
You probably don't know.

14:34.138 --> 14:35.938
The tree that struck
and injured Grandmother

14:37.817 --> 14:39.737
was planted by my mom back then.

14:46.258 --> 14:47.577
She killed my mom,

14:49.298 --> 14:51.138
and now she died under that tree.

14:52.497 --> 14:54.138
You could say it's karma.

14:55.178 --> 14:56.977
Uncle Wenshen, at this Longevity Shop,

14:57.617 --> 15:00.857
what you talk about every day
is just good and evil being repaid.

15:01.538 --> 15:05.138
You chant every day,
yet you still can't see through it?

15:10.704 --> 15:12.624
Good and evil are repaid indeed.

15:15.697 --> 15:19.217
Li, you are very smart.

15:20.577 --> 15:22.418
You don't seem like your father's child.

15:25.258 --> 15:28.378
I'll take that as a compliment from you.

15:30.418 --> 15:34.217
These past days,
I've been tossing and turning.

15:35.664 --> 15:37.008
I've been thinking about you.

15:37.938 --> 15:38.778
About me?

15:39.778 --> 15:43.617
About everything you've done
since you came down the mountain.

15:44.217 --> 15:47.817
You admonished Ms. Wang,
reclaimed your dowry,

15:48.058 --> 15:51.378
and ran Shende Shop so successfully.

15:52.697 --> 15:53.938
You married Prince Ding

15:54.817 --> 15:56.617
and won his favor.

15:57.097 --> 15:59.337
Now, at the Ye residence,

15:59.817 --> 16:03.018
you cleared your mother's name
and avenged her.

16:04.298 --> 16:05.977
These are things I know.

16:07.418 --> 16:08.697
What about the things I don't know?

16:12.778 --> 16:13.857
Someone like you,

16:13.938 --> 16:17.418
so meticulous and cold-hearted,

16:18.178 --> 16:21.337
can turn anyone
into a pawn in your hand.

16:22.138 --> 16:23.538
You came to me today

16:24.538 --> 16:26.977
definitely not just
to tell me this, right?

16:33.058 --> 16:35.018
I heard Jinbao Shop
is no longer mine to run.

16:37.418 --> 16:40.258
And you've given that estate
in the western city to your wife too.

16:43.538 --> 16:44.617
Did you know

16:44.697 --> 16:47.418
how much monthly turnover
a shop on West Market generates?

16:47.898 --> 16:50.538
That's a gold mine of a business.

16:51.058 --> 16:52.817
Not to mention supporting commoners.

16:53.058 --> 16:55.857
Even supporting a hundred mansion guards
would be more than enough.

16:56.418 --> 16:57.737
You gave such a vital lifeline

16:58.018 --> 16:59.497
to someone else so casually?

16:59.737 --> 17:02.138
She is my wife, not someone else.

17:02.778 --> 17:04.777
'She is my wife, not someone else'?

17:05.697 --> 17:07.457
But you told me initially

17:07.537 --> 17:09.618
that too many in court and out
are watching you,

17:09.618 --> 17:10.898
and Ms. Wen can't run things,

17:10.898 --> 17:13.098
so you'd only feel at ease
if it was handed over to me.

17:14.858 --> 17:18.138
Now, just to make a beauty smile,
you gave it away so generously.

17:18.858 --> 17:20.697
Now you don't mind
others eyeing you warily?

17:22.017 --> 17:23.618
Times have changed.

17:25.057 --> 17:27.138
I've even taken on a post
in Jingzhao Prefecture.

17:27.378 --> 17:29.658
Why would I fear them
being wary of me over a few shops?

17:30.257 --> 17:33.178
You're done for.
Mo Xiuyao, you're done for.

17:33.938 --> 17:36.737
How are you different from
a doomed ruler with a wicked favorite?

17:37.497 --> 17:39.697
Giving all your wealth
and power to a beauty.

17:40.017 --> 17:42.098
This is the sign of a fallen country.

17:46.457 --> 17:47.457
Do you still want this?

17:49.297 --> 17:50.138
What's this?

17:50.378 --> 17:53.418
What? Didn't you ask me
to keep investigating your wife?

17:53.418 --> 17:54.338
I found something.

17:54.777 --> 17:57.898
Seeing how lovey-dovey you are now,
it's probably all for nothing.

18:03.818 --> 18:05.737
You won't even take a look?

18:06.497 --> 18:08.658
If she wants to tell me,
she'll come to me on her own.

18:29.737 --> 18:30.537
Mo Xiuyao.

18:34.737 --> 18:37.338
Is something wrong
with my eyes or my brain?

18:37.737 --> 18:38.977
You stood up!

18:39.898 --> 18:41.418
Once healed, I can stand.

18:48.977 --> 18:51.217
It hurts? You can feel pain now?

18:52.418 --> 18:53.898
So you have sensation.

18:54.737 --> 18:56.017
Let me help you walk a bit.

18:56.257 --> 18:57.418
Come on, slowly.

18:57.418 --> 18:58.977
One, two.

18:59.457 --> 19:00.257
Walk a few steps.

19:02.697 --> 19:04.578
Good legs! You've finally stood up.

19:04.578 --> 19:06.378
The heavens
have truly opened their eyes!

19:06.818 --> 19:09.217
Tonight, I'll host a banquet
at Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

19:09.777 --> 19:11.138
Let's drink till we drop!

19:11.138 --> 19:12.057
Keep your voice down.

19:13.537 --> 19:15.737
Don't make it known
that my legs are healed yet.

19:17.777 --> 19:19.178
I'm the first to know?

19:20.098 --> 19:21.818
Your wife sure has skills.

19:21.898 --> 19:23.297
She actually healed your legs.

19:23.777 --> 19:27.057
No wonder. No wonder you gave her
all your family fortune.

19:27.977 --> 19:29.658
This has transcended love.

19:30.098 --> 19:32.338
This is practically a debt of rebirth.

19:33.378 --> 19:35.057
I admit I was narrow-minded.

19:35.418 --> 19:37.017
Not just those few shops.

19:37.418 --> 19:39.777
Even if you gave her
my Qingfeng Mingyue Tower,

19:39.777 --> 19:41.418
I'd be willing to.

19:41.977 --> 19:44.138
Did you come today
to discuss any serious business?

19:44.537 --> 19:47.017
Is there still no news from Huaixi?

19:47.297 --> 19:49.378
In such a mood now, talking about Huaixi

19:49.818 --> 19:51.418
isn't appropriate.

19:53.497 --> 19:56.057
I toast to you with tea instead of wine.

20:02.178 --> 20:03.418
Can we talk business now?

20:03.818 --> 20:04.578
Huaixi.

20:05.578 --> 20:07.138
Once Gongshu Yang arrived in Huaixi,

20:07.138 --> 20:09.578
he's turned that place upside down.

20:09.658 --> 20:11.537
The various clans
were biting at each other.

20:11.578 --> 20:15.378
In the end, they pushed forward
a guard named Qiu as the scapegoat.

20:15.977 --> 20:17.618
He was once the Zhou family's guard

20:17.658 --> 20:19.017
and Marquis Muyang's confidant.

20:19.138 --> 20:21.338
Now he's become a discarded pawn
no one wants.

20:21.457 --> 20:22.378
Will they

20:22.977 --> 20:25.257
let such a man live and talk?

20:25.858 --> 20:28.017
The Zhou family
does have a firm grip on Huaixi.

20:28.336 --> 20:29.618
They won't let Gongshu Yang dig.

20:29.658 --> 20:30.457
Exactly.

20:31.858 --> 20:34.737
They've tried every trick,
soft and hard, overt and covert.

20:36.497 --> 20:39.418
Gongshu Yang still needs
to put in some effort.

20:40.178 --> 20:41.338
But I think

20:41.658 --> 20:44.624
he'll have solid evidence on the Huaixi
weaponry case sooner or later.

20:45.057 --> 20:46.217
After all, behind him

20:46.658 --> 20:49.217
stand the young emperor
and the Empress Dowager.

20:49.257 --> 20:50.938
No one dares to really touch him.

20:51.658 --> 20:53.418
Also, Gongshu Yang
is an upright official.

20:53.578 --> 20:55.977
He won't stop
until he achieves his goal.

21:02.977 --> 21:03.537
Yao,

21:05.098 --> 21:07.658
although our goal
is to bring down Marquis Muyang,

21:08.017 --> 21:10.737
more importantly,
we need to find evidence

21:11.098 --> 21:12.818
to overturn the case
for you, your family,

21:12.858 --> 21:14.777
and the entire Heiyun Cavalry.

21:17.418 --> 21:19.098
What? You want to...

21:20.497 --> 21:22.138
overturn Prince Ding's case?

21:22.977 --> 21:25.977
You want to do something
that even top-rank officials dare not?

21:26.777 --> 21:27.858
Are you crazy?

21:29.178 --> 21:30.178
But why?

21:30.178 --> 21:31.338
Just for Mo Xiuyao?

21:31.497 --> 21:33.217
That's how you think of me?

21:34.338 --> 21:36.217
Does it have to be for a man?

21:36.737 --> 21:39.858
Can't it be for the 30,000 soldiers
who haven't been exonerated?

21:39.977 --> 21:42.138
For the peace and safety
of the common people,

21:42.497 --> 21:44.537
for the majestic authority
of our country,

21:44.777 --> 21:46.457
and for justice and righteousness?

21:51.658 --> 21:54.818
Alright, I am doing it for my mom.

22:00.457 --> 22:03.697
(Hearing my maternal grandfather
had left the mountain)

22:03.858 --> 22:07.098
(and prepared to join forces
with court officials to clear his name,)

22:08.176 --> 22:09.808
(General Xiuwen listened to my mother)

22:10.257 --> 22:11.898
(and revealed the edict's location.)

22:13.138 --> 22:15.057
(But after my mom obtained the edict,)

22:15.728 --> 22:18.000
(it was snatched away
by my father and Uncle Wending.)

22:25.257 --> 22:27.017
Mo Xiuwen died because of that.

22:27.938 --> 22:30.032
The entire Prince Ding's household
was implicated.

22:31.497 --> 22:33.818
And those 30,000 Heiyun Cavalry
who were wronged.

22:34.338 --> 22:35.697
These are all debts my mom

22:36.898 --> 22:39.178
and Lishan Academy owe.

22:39.818 --> 22:41.057
I must repay them.

22:44.257 --> 22:45.658
Now I understand.

22:46.818 --> 22:49.297
Your descent down the mountain
has two purposes.

22:49.697 --> 22:52.017
One is revenge,
and the other is repayment.

22:53.658 --> 22:55.378
You keep your accounts straight.

22:59.537 --> 23:01.098
Then why did you come to me?

23:01.818 --> 23:03.297
If Father is right,

23:04.017 --> 23:07.977
that edict should now
be in Dowager Consort Qin's hands.

23:09.017 --> 23:11.257
Dowager Consort Qin and your master,

23:11.297 --> 23:13.178
Master Xiankun, had a deep bond.

23:13.217 --> 23:15.338
I want to know if you know
about Dowager Consort Qin

23:15.618 --> 23:16.818
and what I should do

23:16.977 --> 23:21.017
to make Dowager Consort Qin
give something so critical to me.

23:31.920 --> 23:32.976
My master

23:33.520 --> 23:36.017
served as an observatory officer
in the Bureau of Astronomy.

23:37.697 --> 23:39.697
When Dowager Consort Qin
was selected as a consort,

23:40.017 --> 23:42.457
my master went as the marriage envoy
to Nanyi to escort her.

23:44.017 --> 23:46.697
It was then that the two of them met.

23:48.217 --> 23:50.818
The renowned dragon painting
of Master Xiankun in Nanyi

23:50.938 --> 23:52.777
happened during
that marriage procession?

23:56.418 --> 23:59.017
Nanyi had suffered a severe drought
for over three years then.

23:59.297 --> 24:01.977
Riverbeds cracked,
and the land was parched.

24:02.618 --> 24:05.057
My master saw corpses
of the starved everywhere,

24:05.098 --> 24:06.178
and the people suffered.

24:06.378 --> 24:07.697
His heart ached for them.

24:08.737 --> 24:11.737
So on the day of the ceremony,
he wielded his brush and painted.

24:13.178 --> 24:15.497
It is said my master's brush
flowed like a dragon.

24:15.737 --> 24:19.257
Soon, a giant dragon appeared
on the paper, vivid and lifelike.

24:19.697 --> 24:21.178
With the final dotting of the eyes,

24:21.537 --> 24:24.457
that giant dragon tore through
the paper and vanished.

24:25.977 --> 24:26.938
In that moment,

24:27.697 --> 24:30.777
thunder roared across the sky,
and dark clouds swirled.

24:32.257 --> 24:33.618
Then the rain fell.

24:36.658 --> 24:37.658
That miraculous? Really?

24:39.938 --> 24:41.777
My master certainly had true abilities.

24:41.977 --> 24:44.618
Dowager Consort Qin
also firmly believed it.

24:47.818 --> 24:48.618
And then what?

24:51.257 --> 24:54.736
From Nanyi to the capital,
they spent several months together.

24:55.777 --> 24:57.898
Under my master's influence,
Dowager Consort Qin

24:58.096 --> 25:00.176
also became obsessed with divination.

25:00.400 --> 25:03.600
Their conversations always revolved
around the Dao of heaven and fate.

25:03.792 --> 25:04.752
Once in the palace,

25:05.072 --> 25:07.977
whenever Dowager Consort Qin
was undecided, she'd consult my master.

25:09.578 --> 25:10.992
But the good times didn't last.

25:11.297 --> 25:13.697
The late emperor died,
and the Eastern Palace was on fire.

25:15.737 --> 25:17.936
My master was implicated
in the Eastern Palace case

25:19.088 --> 25:19.856
and got beheaded.

25:21.418 --> 25:24.898
Master, Consort Qin...
Consort Qin has come to see you.

25:42.537 --> 25:45.017
How did you get involved
with people from the Eastern Palace?

25:46.497 --> 25:48.618
I've managed to see those accusations.

25:49.297 --> 25:51.858
The Eastern Palace people
just randomly implicated others.

25:53.257 --> 25:56.017
But don't worry, the Empress
will figure something out.

26:01.777 --> 26:05.378
Alright, I'll rest assured.

26:09.858 --> 26:13.217
You are truly a fool.

26:16.418 --> 26:17.418
It's a pity

26:19.418 --> 26:21.297
time passes quickly
and can't be relived,

26:22.977 --> 26:24.257
and the world turns.

26:25.578 --> 26:27.378
This is what I should bear.

26:29.618 --> 26:31.057
Don't go to the Empress anymore.

26:32.418 --> 26:33.378
It's useless.

26:33.418 --> 26:35.418
Master, you mustn't give up.

26:35.418 --> 26:35.938
Empress...

26:35.938 --> 26:38.858
Wenshen, you go on ahead.

26:38.858 --> 26:39.618
Master...

26:39.618 --> 26:40.777
I'm fine.

26:42.977 --> 26:46.697
Let us say a few more words.

27:02.418 --> 27:05.057
You said the Empress and I
have linked fates and fortunes.

27:05.057 --> 27:06.818
If I go beg her again, she will help.

27:07.658 --> 27:08.537
It's useless.

27:10.217 --> 27:11.898
Linked fortunes
with the Empress Dowager?

27:12.938 --> 27:14.898
My master divined

27:15.578 --> 27:18.672
that the Empress Dowager's natal star
lights Dowager Consort's Ziwei Palace

27:19.578 --> 27:20.848
as her fated noble one.

27:21.578 --> 27:23.178
Pity the Empress Dowager

27:26.898 --> 27:30.378
couldn't clear my master's name
in the end.

27:30.737 --> 27:33.138
I don't know why
Dowager Consort Qin did that

27:33.618 --> 27:36.017
or why she didn't produce
the testamentary edict.

27:36.618 --> 27:37.618
But now,

27:37.898 --> 27:40.592
it won't be easy
to get her to hand it over.

27:43.378 --> 27:44.938
It will naturally take some measures.

27:47.578 --> 27:49.017
Have you figured out what to do?

27:50.737 --> 27:52.257
I have to rely on Master Xiankun.

27:53.858 --> 27:54.858
On my master?

27:57.297 --> 27:59.984
Let's wait for an opportune moment.
Heaven will help us.

28:05.872 --> 28:07.696
(Marquis Muyang's Mansion)

28:14.057 --> 28:16.138
Can't hold on
after just this short time?

28:16.537 --> 28:19.737
Didn't Guard Qin
usually train you people?

28:21.057 --> 28:21.977
Higher.

28:27.938 --> 28:28.777
Just ahead.

28:41.658 --> 28:42.537
Guard Qin.

28:53.578 --> 28:54.297
Young Lord.

28:54.658 --> 28:55.737
Long time no see.

28:55.898 --> 28:57.578
Have you been busy?

28:57.938 --> 28:58.737
Young Lord,

28:59.777 --> 29:02.697
Marquis Muyang instructed me
to run an errand. I just got back.

29:03.418 --> 29:04.578
Well done.

29:05.488 --> 29:08.537
You're deeply valued by my father.
The capable should do more.

29:08.737 --> 29:10.898
Unlike me, who's just a hedonist.

29:11.217 --> 29:14.537
Idle all day, I can only drink
and make merry here.

29:15.457 --> 29:16.697
It's quite boring.

29:16.898 --> 29:18.057
Please don't say that.

29:19.938 --> 29:21.777
You came just in time today.

29:22.378 --> 29:23.938
I have fresh mutton here.

29:24.178 --> 29:27.297
Guard Qin, why not sit down
and drink with me? How about it?

29:27.497 --> 29:28.938
I have urgent matters to attend to,

29:29.098 --> 29:30.977
so I won't disturb your enjoyment.

29:35.818 --> 29:36.618
I take my leave.

29:42.418 --> 29:44.138
You are very disapproving, Guard Qin.

29:44.697 --> 29:46.697
That's not good.

29:47.098 --> 29:49.737
Pork is fatty, mutton is savory,

29:50.578 --> 29:53.658
and beef is quite chewy.

29:54.378 --> 29:56.297
Each has its merits and drawbacks,
hard to rank.

29:57.418 --> 29:59.497
But they say men
are the paragon of all beings,

30:00.098 --> 30:03.497
and human flesh
combines the best of all things.

30:04.257 --> 30:06.138
Roasted, it is supremely delicious.

30:06.297 --> 30:07.658
The meat isn't even cooked yet.

30:08.378 --> 30:11.537
Guard Qin, how can you leave now?

30:22.017 --> 30:23.777
Young Lord!

30:24.898 --> 30:26.938
I've been looking for you.

30:27.457 --> 30:29.138
Registrar Tan has returned,

30:29.497 --> 30:31.418
bringing a letter from your mother

30:31.418 --> 30:34.057
and all sorts of delicacies
from Lingnan.

30:34.057 --> 30:35.977
All the good food and wine
you could ask for.

30:36.178 --> 30:39.658
Young Lord, come with me
and take a look quickly.

30:41.578 --> 30:44.618
Also, Marquis Muyang has returned.

30:47.297 --> 30:49.378
He's waiting for you in the main hall.

30:52.178 --> 30:53.098
Blockhead.

30:54.017 --> 30:55.057
Let's go now.

30:56.697 --> 30:59.418
Young Lord,
Lingnan is thousands of li away.

30:59.418 --> 31:02.138
How did Registrar Tan
bring those things back?

31:02.217 --> 31:04.016
Later, ask him properly for me.

31:04.080 --> 31:05.098
Alright.

31:31.098 --> 31:31.938
Watching fish?

31:50.457 --> 31:51.457
Carefree and easy.

32:05.217 --> 32:06.658
Let's go back.

32:07.777 --> 32:10.578
On my way here,
I didn't see many servants.

32:10.618 --> 32:11.697
Where did everyone go?

32:12.297 --> 32:14.178
Today I sent them all
to Qiongying Residence.

32:24.898 --> 32:27.497
From now on, among the servants,
only Jin, Ding,

32:27.777 --> 32:30.057
and your Qingyu, Tao, and Xing

32:30.217 --> 32:31.257
can enter the inner court.

32:31.618 --> 32:33.697
No one else can enter.

32:34.378 --> 32:35.178
Why?

32:37.338 --> 32:40.777
The fact that my legs are healed
must stay hidden for now.

32:45.858 --> 32:48.697
No wonder you won't let me remove
those iron rings in your room,

32:49.057 --> 32:50.297
and you've kept the wheelchair.

32:51.017 --> 32:53.457
So you're playing the pig
to outwit the tiger.

32:56.497 --> 32:59.378
Tomorrow I must have Qingyu
buy a pigskin at the market

32:59.578 --> 33:01.578
to drape over you,
a tiger pretending to be sick.

33:06.378 --> 33:07.697
You are absolutely right.

33:13.017 --> 33:14.378
Where did you go today?

33:15.618 --> 33:16.537
Longevity Shop.

33:17.658 --> 33:19.138
Did you make up with Uncle Wenshen?

33:21.138 --> 33:22.138
Not really.

33:22.818 --> 33:25.697
No matter what,
Grandmother died because of me.

33:26.497 --> 33:29.858
As her son,
he must have some resentment.

33:30.697 --> 33:32.138
But Uncle Wenshen is a good man,

33:32.737 --> 33:35.057
clear-minded and reasonable.

33:35.898 --> 33:37.297
He should be able to understand me.

33:38.818 --> 33:40.178
You did nothing wrong.

33:40.818 --> 33:42.297
Don't feel guilty toward him.

33:44.017 --> 33:45.697
I don't feel guilty at all.

33:46.858 --> 33:50.138
I was confident and left him speechless.

33:51.618 --> 33:53.378
I won't let myself
be taken advantage of.

33:54.178 --> 33:55.737
You don't need to console me.

34:05.217 --> 34:08.298
By the way, you said
only Qingyu, Tao, and Xing

34:08.298 --> 34:10.858
can enter this courtyard from now on.

34:11.418 --> 34:12.738
Why not Qingshuang?

34:16.017 --> 34:16.818
Qingshuang?

34:17.258 --> 34:18.057
Yes.

34:19.577 --> 34:22.657
Qingshuang endured so many years
of hardship with me on Lishan Mountain.

34:22.898 --> 34:24.338
Now we've left the mountain together

34:24.418 --> 34:25.898
and entered this mansion together.

34:26.258 --> 34:27.898
She is the person closest to me.

34:28.698 --> 34:31.698
Qingyu and the others
can freely enter Tuisi Pavilion.

34:31.818 --> 34:33.137
Why can't Qingshuang?

34:37.298 --> 34:38.298
Don't worry.

34:38.497 --> 34:41.298
She won't spill that you're pretending
to be a cripple.

34:45.537 --> 34:46.898
Right, Qingshuang?

34:56.137 --> 34:56.898
Let's eat.

35:01.577 --> 35:02.378
Let's eat.

35:13.177 --> 35:15.898
Your Highness,
haven't you already asked once?

35:15.898 --> 35:18.137
There's no maid named Qingshuang
in the mansion at all.

35:19.017 --> 35:21.698
Qingshuang is the maid
my wife has kept since childhood.

35:22.057 --> 35:23.778
She went up Lishan Mountain with her,

35:24.298 --> 35:25.698
left with her upon the edict,

35:25.778 --> 35:27.298
and accompanied her into the mansion.

35:27.898 --> 35:29.137
Did you check thoroughly?

35:29.577 --> 35:30.698
Then it's even more wrong.

35:31.017 --> 35:34.698
The Empress Dowager's edict allowed
only Her Highness to leave to marry.

35:35.057 --> 35:37.938
The mountain guards
acted according to the edict.

35:38.378 --> 35:41.738
No one else but Her Highness
could have left the mountain.

36:13.657 --> 36:14.818
First moon, twelfth day,

36:14.818 --> 36:16.176
(Lishan Academy)
Ye Li left Lishan Mountain alone

36:16.176 --> 36:17.177
with the edict.

36:19.536 --> 36:21.488
(Lishan Mountain
is 100 li from the capital.)

36:21.818 --> 36:24.577
(Ye Li was penniless
and found it hard to move.)

36:25.057 --> 36:27.457
- (Probably, the mountain guards helped)
- Farewell.

36:27.457 --> 36:28.738
- (and raised money for her)
- I'll come back to see you again.

36:28.977 --> 36:30.457
(so she could ride in an ox cart.)

36:30.657 --> 36:33.218
(After days of bumpy travel,
she finally reached the capital.)

36:34.577 --> 36:36.617
- (At Changxing Gate,)
- Young lady,

36:36.617 --> 36:39.057
- (Ye Li seemed to ask for directions.)
- where are we going now?

36:39.577 --> 36:40.877
- (Then she reached the tea stall west)
- I need to get to

36:40.877 --> 36:42.378
- (of the mansion gate)
- Prince Ding's Mansion.

36:42.704 --> 36:43.728
- (to rest.)
- What would you like?

36:43.728 --> 36:45.137
- (She asked for some honey cakes.)
- Thank you.

36:45.698 --> 36:49.177
(Then she asked about the mansion
and how you've been.)

36:49.657 --> 36:51.298
(The stall owner can testify.)

36:52.137 --> 36:52.898
You eat too.

36:52.898 --> 36:56.137
(Only when the sun set did Ye Li leave)

36:56.258 --> 36:57.418
(and go to the Ye Mansion.)

36:58.537 --> 37:00.137
(The road was long and difficult.)

37:01.298 --> 37:02.457
(Ye Li, a frail woman,)

37:02.698 --> 37:05.577
(reached the capital alone
after many hardships.)

37:06.577 --> 37:09.338
(If you have a heart,
you should cherish her.)

37:09.977 --> 37:11.298
Descended Lishan Mountain alone.

37:13.218 --> 37:14.657
Arrived in the capital alone.

37:24.858 --> 37:26.338
Here, this is delicious.

37:28.898 --> 37:31.898
You don't like this taste?
Then I'll eat it.

37:46.378 --> 37:47.497
Want some candy?

37:47.657 --> 37:48.537
I'm not eating.

37:50.258 --> 37:52.338
Then wait for me a bit.
Let's go for a walk.

37:53.898 --> 37:56.537
(When you see tiny whirlpools
on the water surface,)

37:57.177 --> 38:00.258
(the deep undercurrent has already
turned thousands of circles.)

38:01.360 --> 38:02.416
(Thinking carefully,)

38:03.856 --> 38:05.168
(she's been this way for ages.)

38:10.577 --> 38:12.457
(She always talks to herself.)

38:12.818 --> 38:14.537
Qingshuang, you feed it.

38:14.858 --> 38:17.776
(At first I thought
it was just a habit of hers.)

38:19.017 --> 38:21.776
(After all, she has so many
unusual thoughts and behaviors.)

38:22.698 --> 38:25.738
(Talking to herself
really isn't a big deal.)

38:25.818 --> 38:26.657
Eat this.

38:27.698 --> 38:29.738
I won't eat this. I'll eat that.

38:31.057 --> 38:32.378
These shrimp are so fresh.

38:32.577 --> 38:34.457
My lady, you should eat more.

38:34.457 --> 38:35.698
That way you'll stay healthy.

38:35.888 --> 38:36.858
You too.

38:37.360 --> 38:38.938
After you finish, I'll sing for you.

38:39.818 --> 38:40.938
(But now it seems)

38:41.552 --> 38:44.898
(those words of hers
weren't for herself.)

38:46.577 --> 38:50.128
(In her eyes, there is someone
who has always been by her side.)

38:50.457 --> 38:51.258
What's this?

38:51.258 --> 38:52.778
(She would eat with her,)

38:53.497 --> 38:54.898
(read with her,)

38:55.698 --> 38:59.152
(and keep her company through
the dull moments of ordinary days.)

38:59.378 --> 39:00.656
I use it to test medicine.

39:03.472 --> 39:05.298
I'll try it on you later.

39:06.258 --> 39:07.218
It works great.

39:08.418 --> 39:12.177
(From dawn to dusk,
she has never been alone.)

39:22.378 --> 39:23.824
Catch a big one for Her Highness.

39:24.818 --> 39:25.778
Qingshuang, look.

39:28.137 --> 39:29.040
Let me teach you.

39:31.898 --> 39:34.698
In your opinion,
why is my wife like that?

39:37.617 --> 39:38.497
Your Highness,

39:39.137 --> 39:41.378
Her Highness is probably too lonely.

39:42.258 --> 39:43.698
Isn't that a kind of illness?

39:44.778 --> 39:46.177
You could call it an illness,

39:46.537 --> 39:49.298
but the root is in the heart,
not the body.

39:50.778 --> 39:53.298
I've practiced medicine
for years and have heard

39:53.657 --> 39:55.218
when someone suffers a sudden shock,

39:55.218 --> 39:57.698
like losing a close
family member or friend,

39:57.778 --> 40:00.497
they may find it unbearable
and hallucinate,

40:01.298 --> 40:03.258
seeing them vividly before their eyes

40:03.537 --> 40:05.457
and believing them still alive
and never gone.

40:06.298 --> 40:07.938
Then isn't Her Highness mad?

40:11.137 --> 40:12.738
It can't just be called madness.

40:14.057 --> 40:15.258
As Your Highness said,

40:15.537 --> 40:16.938
she went up the mountain young

40:17.378 --> 40:19.298
and was like sisters
with her personal maid.

40:19.898 --> 40:21.537
Then she suddenly left the mountain

40:21.698 --> 40:23.738
and traveled all the way
to the capital alone,

40:23.977 --> 40:26.698
with no one close
in her maternal family to confide in.

40:26.778 --> 40:27.858
She must be heartbroken.

40:28.818 --> 40:31.577
Her Highness is still young
and couldn't cope for a while.

40:32.057 --> 40:34.938
It's within reason that she conjured
an image of someone close.

40:35.617 --> 40:38.378
In this situation,
apart from the delusion,

40:38.898 --> 40:42.497
her words, actions, and dealings
are no different from ordinary people.

40:43.057 --> 40:46.698
Simply put, she's just
deeply heartbroken,

40:46.778 --> 40:49.497
seeking a bit of solace for herself.

40:50.858 --> 40:52.137
How should it be treated?

40:52.457 --> 40:54.057
Any quick-acting method?

40:54.698 --> 40:55.938
No good cure comes from haste.

40:56.298 --> 40:58.977
Moreover, this is a hidden scar,
not curable by medicine.

40:59.137 --> 41:00.457
It should be addressed gradually.

41:00.938 --> 41:03.537
For now, ensure she rests well,

41:03.657 --> 41:06.057
watch her diet,
and keep her mind at ease.

41:06.858 --> 41:09.657
Most importantly, give her heart
something to hold onto,

41:09.657 --> 41:10.898
so she no longer feels lonely.

41:11.378 --> 41:13.097
Family members should
keep her more company.

41:13.577 --> 41:16.457
Over time, she may gradually recover.

41:23.938 --> 41:25.338
More company.

41:32.176 --> 41:35.888
(Lishan Academy)

41:37.584 --> 41:40.880
♪Will be romantic in your eyes♪

41:44.898 --> 41:47.057
You're here. What did you bring?

41:49.218 --> 41:51.137
I had ginseng soup made
for you this morning.

41:55.177 --> 41:56.057
What are you writing?

41:56.938 --> 41:58.657
A letter. A family letter.

42:04.258 --> 42:05.218
To Lishan Mountain?

42:05.818 --> 42:06.617
Yes.

42:10.177 --> 42:11.977
What? No peeking.

42:12.418 --> 42:13.338
Drink the soup first.

42:13.338 --> 42:14.457
Go over there first.

42:15.738 --> 42:16.698
You have to rewrite it.

42:18.298 --> 42:19.418
Let me do it.

42:23.057 --> 42:24.298
Luckily, the inside isn't wet.

42:25.537 --> 42:28.617
Just sit tight and don't make trouble.

42:30.577 --> 42:31.577
Drink the soup first.

42:34.544 --> 42:37.488
♪From all the world,
we share a cup of tea♪

42:37.488 --> 42:39.728
♪Small as the fragrance of a flower♪

42:39.728 --> 42:42.448
♪To share it with you♪

42:43.728 --> 42:46.352
(Preview)

42:46.778 --> 42:47.657
What's wrong?

42:48.497 --> 42:49.698
You've been acting strange.

42:51.698 --> 42:54.097
Li, in the mansion now,

42:54.577 --> 42:56.017
do you still feel lonely?

42:56.378 --> 42:57.657
Was it that night?

42:57.657 --> 42:58.698
Send her away.

42:59.258 --> 43:02.418
Last midnight, a sudden fire
broke out at Prince Li's Mansion.

43:02.818 --> 43:04.858
The fire spread too fast to be put out.

43:05.698 --> 43:06.640
Prince Li has died.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
